<TrainingDetailsVTwo ID="x15004" Name="News Archive" Layout="default-training_v2.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">News Archive</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">An archive of all News Articles published by an office.</Abstract><TrainingImage type="imagefile" label="Page Type Image" hidden="false" readonly="false" required="false" Expanded="true" AlternateText="" Border="" HSpace="" VSpace="" Width="300" Height="528" Alignment="">Internal_Use/Ingeniux_Training/Template Thumbnails/generalNewsArchive.jpg</TrainingImage><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<h3>Proper Use</h3>
<p>This page organizes a directory of articles in an archive format. It collects all News Articles from an indicated source and displays the date and abstract, sorting them by publication date.<br />The News Navigation Component is used to select the directory start page and depth of the directory you want to display. http://beta.byui.edu/newsroom/news-archive (x84) is a good example of its use.</p>
<h3>Audience</h3>
<p>Varies</p>
<h3>Intended Authors</h3>
<p>All advanced authors (editors).</p>
